Company Overview of Zurich Life Assurance plc



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Zurich Life Assurance plc provides life and general insurance products for customers in Ireland. The company offers individual and employer pension plans; personal savings for a house or car, and kids' future; and investments solutions. It also provides life insurance solutions, including family protection, such as term protection, pension term protection, and whole of life cover; mortgage protection; and business protection, which include key person insurance, co-director insurance, corporate co-director insurance, partnership insurance, and group risk. In addition, the company offers various funds, including multi-asset, cash and bond, equity, property, alternatives, and closed funds. Zuri...
Zurich Life Assurance plc provides life and general insurance products for customers in Ireland. The company offers individual and employer pension plans; personal savings for a house or car, and kids' future; and investments solutions. It also provides life insurance solutions, including family protection, such as term protection, pension term protection, and whole of life cover; mortgage protection; and business protection, which include key person insurance, co-director insurance, corporate co-director insurance, partnership insurance, and group risk. In addition, the company offers various funds, including multi-asset, cash and bond, equity, property, alternatives, and closed funds. Zurich Life Assurance plc was formerly known as Eagle Star Life Assurance Company of Ireland Limited and changed its name to Zurich Life Assurance plc in August 2009. The company was founded in 1977 and is headquartered in Blackrock, Ireland. Zurich Life Assurance plc operates as a subsidiary of Zurich Insurance Group Ltd.
